	<FactionDef ParentName="WH_SukiradaeFactionBase">
		<defName>WH_SukiradaeTribe</defName>
		<label>tribal scavengers</label>
		<description>A loose confederation of tribal scavengers who've agreed to mostly fight outsiders rather than each other. Driven by a blood-and-honor culture, they value personal strength and ruthlessness. In any case, tribal scavengers are a mostly nomadic people who live off the land using primitive tools and weapons.</description>
		<factionIconPath>World/WorldObjects/Expanding/Pueblo</factionIconPath>
		<colorSpectrum>
			<li>(0.85,0.00,0.25)</li>
			<li>(0.42,0.05,0.68)</li>
		</colorSpectrum>
	</FactionDef>
	
